        to create the form field to add employer information to the job.

        This field should be a dropdown menu with all of the employers in the database. (<select>)

        In addition, add a link to the <div> element to add new employers. (ASP CONTROLLER ACTION ADD)
        This way, if a user doesn’t see the employer they are looking for,
